metadata.name: White
metadata.description:
Work White, 2020 
Hybrids series 

The work was shown in the exhibition *UND DAS IST AUCH GUT SO.  [Galerie Judith Andreae, Bonn](https://www.galerie-andreae.de/artists/victoria-pidust/) 
and in the exhibition open-ended photography [Robert Morat, Berlin](https://www.robertmorat.de/artists/pidust-victoria/)

Other works from this series were presented on Paris Photo 2021 with reviews on [AnOther](https://www.anothermag.com/art-photography/13714/three-artists-you-need-to-know-from-photoworks-director-shoair-mavlian), [NÃºmero](https://www.numero.com/fr/photographie/paris-photo-curiosa-victoria-pidust-john-yuyi-prince-gyasi-shilo-karolina-wojtas) and [PHOTONEWS](https://photonews.de/zeitung/november-2021/),
included in [Mart Stam Preis 2020](https://www.verlag-kettler.de/de/buecher/mart-stam-preis-2020/)
